_sText:
This is the 3rd edition gg_malreynolds I made for the Aerelon server and named after myself. Version 2 has been on the server for a long time now and I wanted to update it with new geometry and make it look nicer. Also took some feedback from players and implemented them.

The map is mostly Dev Textures, because I really cannot texture, but found that when playing with textures the underground lost the golden light and I thought that looked nice, so kept the default Orange Dev Texture to achieve it.

Players: 30

Dev textures from FPSBanana http://www.fpsbanana.com/ by Chris528. Thanks for the textures.

Custom Textures and Nav file included
